lass=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399700/extras/a05b3a21e02174f72d3f73e26ada25e3.webp?t=1760106062\" width=301 height=32 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399700/extras/fdba42236effe305cef0e9638ada7181.poster.avif?t=1760106062\" width=600 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399700/extras/fdba42236effe305cef0e9638ada7181.webm?t=1760106062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399700/extras/fdba42236effe305cef0e9638ada7181.mp4?t=1760106062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >People whose needs go unsatisfied will hold a grudge against your rule. Some of them will become dissidents and radicals. They will form secret societies to overthrow you. Protests on the streets will turn into massacres and riots. You have to make a tough choice of which class to support and which to suppress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399700/extras/efedae809942e1c420cbf34f127f1c98.webp?t=1760106062\" width=300 height=32 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399700/extras/fedb590d001e37110c2533adaf7f3560.poster.avif?t=1760106062\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399700/extras/fedb590d001e37110c2533adaf7f3560.webm?t=1760106062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://